t YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">当一地碎黄随深秋的凉风厌厌舞动的时候，万物已经开始默默无奈地蛰伏于往昔的尘埃，不知悲喜，不闻凉热，只企及躲过寒冬的虐杀，在下一个轮回里能够重生，在又一个春天里获得希望。还有许多生命，在这深秋的季节里，就如这远山的斑斓，泛出生命最后的色彩，没有希望只有感叹。因为，下一个轮回，已经不属于它们。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">多像层林浸染，越是苍凉，越是斑斓，生是希望，死是烂漫。在飘落的序幕里，让灿烂登场，给壮丽醒目。这一切都是为了逝去的记住。就像渔歌唱晚，欸乃着疲倦的撸声，依依不舍地飘向彼岸。虽然“晚风翼翼浪吹衣，凉水鳞鳞翠入微，”尽管船舱里还泛着银色的鳞光，夜还是来了，疲倦和归去是渔翁的必然。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">深秋时节望远山，远山斑斓。</span>\n</