夕阳，只有一个真理：抓住时光，让每一天辉煌。就像深秋的远山，依旧尽情地斑斓。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">这斑斓，留给远山，留给记忆，也留给自己。</span>\n</p>', '<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">深秋时节望远山，远山斑斓。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"color:#333333;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;text-align:justify;background:#F8F8F8;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:黑体;font-size:18px;color:#FF9900;\">一个季节的终结，蕴含了几个季节的追求和希望，也凝聚了几多时光演绎的快乐、痛苦和沧桑。这一切